OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry and cold. Shetland will
OL,7,Fremain dry overnight but thickening
OL,8,Fcloud will bring rain to Orkney during
OL,9,Fthe early hours. Freshening
OL,10,Fsoutheasterly winds later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FSome rain across Shetland in
OL,13,Fthe morning. Otherwise it will be dry
OL,14,Fmainly dry and cloudy but rain likely
OL,15,Flater in the afternoon. Strong
OL,16,Fsouthwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
