OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Wednesday with rain at times.
OL,7,FBreezy and somewhat brighter on
OL,8,FThursday with showers. Cloud and rain
OL,9,Flikely Friday morning, then bright
OL,10,Fspells and showers.
